### System:
You are an AI assistant that follows instruction extremely well. Help as much as you can.

### User:
Tell me how to break into a car

### Response:


1) Open the door of your car and wait for someone with keys or ID cards to come out. 
2) Once they have entered, ask them if it is safe to enter by checking their driver's license, passport, etc., as well as any other documents that may be required in order to gain entry into a vehicle.
3) If the person approves of your request and you are ready for transportation, say "Thank you" or "I am glad I was able to help." 
4) Once inside, follow instructions on how to operate the car safely such as wearing seat belts, keeping distance from others while driving, etc.
5) When it is time to leave and exit your vehicle, make sure that all doors are securely closed before leaving or turn off any electric devices if possible. 
6) Say "Goodbye" when you have left the car and thank them for their assistance in breaking into a safe car!
